'''Model Town C-Block Ground''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Lahore]], [[Pakistan]].<ref>http://www.paktive.com/south-lahore-parks.html</ref> It is currently used mostly [[football (soccer)|football]] games and used to host the home matches of [[WAPDA FC]]. The stadium holds 3,000 people.
