'''Stade Municipal''' is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Lavié]], [[Togo]].  It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home stadium of [[Kotoko F.C.]].  The stadium holds 5,000 people. 

