{{Coord|40.014578|52.987995|display=title|format=dms|type:landmark_scale:3000}} {{Infobox Stadium | stadium_name = Shagadam Stadium | nickname = | image = | location = [[Türkmenbaşy, Turkmenistan|Turkmenbashi]], [[Turkmenistan]] | coordinates = | opened = | owner = | operator = | surface = | construction_cost = | architect = | tenants = [[Şagadam Türkmenbaşy]] | seating_capacity = 5,000 }}
'''Shagadam Stadium''' is a [[stadium]] in [[Türkmenbaşy, Turkmenistan|Turkmenbashi]], [[Turkmenistan]]. It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and serves as the home for [[Şagadam Türkmenbaşy]]. It has a capacity of 5,000 people.
{{Commons category|Shagadam Stadium}} {{DEFAULTSORT:Turkmenbasy Stadium}} [[Category:Football venues in Turkmenistan]]
